Nic'Epona (singular and plural), or Epona's daughters, are are said to be direct descendents of Epona, the horse-goddess of the Celtic Pantheon. They resemble horses of any color of the rainbow; they can change their coloration at will. 
They're defenders of Tir na Og in the Outlands. Every one of the nic'Epona are female, reproducing by breeding with other equine creatures. 

